<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1920,2042]" lastBlockId="6.[151,1437,150,2037]" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="525" pageId="5" pageNumber="524">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,207,2016,2042]" pageId="5" pageNumber="524">Note</emphasis>
: While proposing synonymy between 
<taxonomicName authority="Curtis, 1845" authorityName="Curtis" authorityYear="1845" box="[646,1041,2015,2042]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Alphitobius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="524" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctatus">
<emphasis box="[646,893,2015,2041]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="524">Alphitobius punctatus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Curtis, J." box="[901,1041,2015,2042]" pageId="5" pageNumber="524" pagination="441 - 476" refId="ref8290" refString="Curtis, J. (1845) Descriptions, &amp; c. of the insects collected by Captain P. P. King in the survey of the Straits of Magellan. Transactions of the Linnean Society of London, 19, 441 - 476. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1096 - 3642.1842. tb 00371. x" type="journal article" year="1845">Curtis, 1845</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Solier, 1851" authorityName="Solier" authorityYear="1851" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Blapstinus" kingdom="Animalia" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="525" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="524" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctulatus">
<emphasis box="[1098,1355,2015,2041]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="524">Blapstinus punctulatus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Solier, A. J." lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="525" pageId="5" pageNumber="524" pagination="5 - 285" refId="ref10194" refString="Solier, A. J. (1851) Insectos. Coleopteros. In: Historia fisica y politica de Chile segun documentos adquiridos en esta republica durante doce anos de residencia en ella y publicada bajo los auspicios del supremo gobierno por Claudio Gay. Zoologia. Tomo Quinto. Museo de Historia Natural de Santiago, Paris, pp. 5 - 285." type="book chapter" year="1851">Solier, 1851</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, to avoid secondary homonymy with 
<taxonomicName authority="(Fabricius)" baseAuthorityName="Fabricius" box="[648,1020,151,178]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Blapstinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="525" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctatus">
<emphasis box="[648,885,151,177]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="525">Blapstinus punctatus</emphasis>
(Fabricius)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Gebien, H." box="[1034,1199,151,177]" pageId="6" pageNumber="525" pagination="283 - 314" refId="ref8544" refString="Gebien, H. (1938) Katalog der Tenebrioniden. Teil II. Mitteilungen der Munchener Entomologischen Gesellschaft, 28, 283 - 314. [kat. 402 - 433]" type="journal article" year="1938">Gebien (1938)</bibRefCitation>
rejected 
<taxonomicName authority="Curtis, 1845" authorityName="Curtis" authorityYear="1845" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Alphitobius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="525" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctatus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="525">Alphitobius punctatus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Curtis, J." box="[270,412,186,213]" pageId="6" pageNumber="525" pagination="441 - 476" refId="ref8290" refString="Curtis, J. (1845) Descriptions, &amp; c. of the insects collected by Captain P. P. King in the survey of the Straits of Magellan. Transactions of the Linnean Society of London, 19, 441 - 476. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1096 - 3642.1842. tb 00371. x" type="journal article" year="1845">Curtis, 1845</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and replaced it with its oldest available synonym— 
<taxonomicName authority="Solier, 1851" authorityName="Solier" authorityYear="1851" box="[1021,1432,186,213]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Blapstinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="525" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctulatus">
<emphasis box="[1021,1280,187,213]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="525">Blapstinus punctulatus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Solier, A. J." box="[1290,1432,186,213]" pageId="6" pageNumber="525" pagination="5 - 285" refId="ref10194" refString="Solier, A. J. (1851) Insectos. Coleopteros. In: Historia fisica y politica de Chile segun documentos adquiridos en esta republica durante doce anos de residencia en ella y publicada bajo los auspicios del supremo gobierno por Claudio Gay. Zoologia. Tomo Quinto. Museo de Historia Natural de Santiago, Paris, pp. 5 - 285." type="book chapter" year="1851">Solier, 1851</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. According to the regulations of ICZN (1999), particularly art. 59.3, a junior secondary homonym replaced before 1961 is permanently invalid unless the substitute name is not in use and the relevant taxa are no longer considered congeneric. As a result the valid name of the below redescribed species is 
<taxonomicName authority="(Solier)" authorityName="Kamiński &amp; Lumen &amp; Kanda &amp; Smith" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Kamiński &amp; Lumen &amp; Kanda &amp; Smith" baseAuthorityYear="1851" box="[982,1305,295,322]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Lodinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="525" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctulatus">
<emphasis box="[982,1210,295,321]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="525">Lodinus punctulatus</emphasis>
(Solier)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
